rawContent:
Soooo…apparently I need a DNA test and extensive brain scanning / study to help my #psychologist & #psychiatrist try and get even a clue to help my #anxiety & #depression. They looked at my file and both were like “you weren’t lying when you said you tried everything”.

Everything but scanning my brain I guess. Did a DNA test before, didn’t really show anything but I can’t get the results back from the place I did it with.(how do you lose medical records?!)

This is gonna be an interesting next couple of months. Trying to be optimistic. I just wanna feel like my good old self again. Life makes that pretty hard sometimes, for everyone, eh? Guess it’s my turn.

Time for late lunch.
